resources.name: Detailed information on public opinion website

description:
This report is the second wave of three surveys relating to a major information campaign about consumers‟ rights, which itself consists of three waves. The aim of the three surveys is to track trends in public opinion, and to measure the effects of the campaign on the target group, the 21 to 45 year-old. The fieldwork for this second wave of the survey took place from 14-18 May 2009.
The fieldwork for the wave 3 of the survey took place from 2-6 November 2009.
#####The results by volumes are distributed as follows:
* Volume A: Countries
* Volume AA: Groups of countries
* Volume A' (AP): Trends
* Volume AA' (AAP): Trends of groups of countries
* Volume B: EU/socio-demographics
* Volume C: Country/socio-demographics
title: Flash Eurobarometer 268: Comsumer Protection and Consumer Rights (Waves 2 and 3) - Estonia Lituania Latvia
name: S797_268
alternative_title: Consumer rights - Information campaigns EE, LV, LT
